20 // Perform steps to resume generator after `value` is resolved.

22 // closure. `on_resolve` is the SharedFunctioninfo instance used to create the
23 // resolve closure. Returns the Promise-wrapped `value`.

29
30 // Return a new built-in function object as defined in

33 TNode<Boolean> done);
34
35 private:
36 void InitializeNativeClosure(TNode<Context> context,
37 TNode<NativeContext> native_context,
38 TNode<HeapObject> function,
39 TNode<SharedFunctionInfo> shared_info);
40 TNode<Context> AllocateAsyncIteratorValueUnwrapContext(
41 TNode<NativeContext> native_context, TNode<Boolean> done);
42};
